Setup Steps
Clone the repository
Bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/smart-home-controller.git
cd smart-home-controller


Verify Java and Maven
Bash
java --version
mvn --version


Build the project
Bash
mvn clean compile


Run tests
Bash
mvn test


Start the application
Bash
mvn exec:java



